                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d690">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Gummeré</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tangier</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-11-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 19, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>German minister informs me Spanish minister is directed by Spanish Government to
                    obtain the consent of Moorish Government to the meeting of the conference at
                    Algeciras on December 15. Germany and France support this request.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gummeré.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
